{"tid":1896397,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[抑鬱症工具] 心之流 HK Flow Tool","createTime":"2020-02-25T06:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T06:41:06.000Z","uid":288075,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e5f50715dae479a0e16d9c245a7308e5c8cf1a35","tid":1896397,"uid":288075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:04:00.000Z","msg":"無意間o係fb見到呢個網:<br />\n心之流[HK FLOW Tool] 係一個由香港大學李嘉誠醫學院精神醫學系(青少年精神健康小組) 整嘅不記名工具。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hku.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_6zEJ0R1E6aLqyJn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhku.au1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_6zEJ0R1E6aLqyJn&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpYDCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=91530b9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hku.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_6zEJ0R1E6aLqyJn</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係節錄:<br />\n有抑鬱症嘅時候，大腦進入咗另一種狀態，令我哋可能會：<br />\n<br />\n    做嘢變得好慢（例如學校/公司嘅嘢、跟唔上其他人）<br />\n    成日覺得好攰、冇動力做嘢<br />\n    變得孤立（想收埋自己，唔想見人/參與群體活動）<br />\n    集中唔到精神（特別係上堂/返工、做功課、同朋友傾計可能要聽幾次先明）<br />\n    記憶力變差（唔記得啲可能好重要嘅嘢）<br />\n    做唔到決定<br />\n    瞓得好差、長時間地瞓唔著，又或者成日瞓，但瞓極都唔精神<br />\n    冇胃口（或暴食；長時間唔處理可以導致身體機能同認知能力出現好大問題）<br />\n<br />\n大家都可試下，我結果係中度抑鬱...<br />\n以上徵狀我都幾乎中哂..."},{"pid":"09e03781ca3472a62124ef9e06e6a0675b6669f6","tid":1896397,"uid":120458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:07:32.000Z","msg":"呢個工具係好掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbdceae041bbe904a1cd324f11a6d8d9490fac5","tid":1896397,"uid":179990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"好有用 仲有得跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}